title: Add btriunpack and update the btrifact test to use it.
body_html: I'm open to changes in the interface. I included mode for efficiency so that both aren't extracted if somebody only needs one. I included dtype for convenience because when only the pivots are being extracted, there is no way to know the type of the main LU data because the pivots are ints.

body: I'm open to changes in the interface. I included `mode` for efficiency so that both aren't extracted if somebody only needs one. I included `dtype` for convenience because when only the pivots are being extracted, there is no way to know the type of the main LU data because the pivots are ints.
